\f0\i0 \cf2 But many Yale students are desperate to remain at the Ivy League college. Rachael Shaw-Rosenbaum was one of them.\
\
\'93I have attempted suicide 3 times in the past 3 days and have not stopped thinking about it,\'94 she wrote on Reddit on March 16, 2021. \'93What do I do? If I go to the hospital again this year, I will be academically withdrawn from my university...\'94\
\
